      "raw_text": "PORTLAND, Ore, July 22.-Dol-\nlar wheat and Sc flour are again in\nsight-likewise smaller loaves of\nbread for consumers. With wheat\nprices advancing daily both here\nand in Chicago, with Liverpool, Ber-\nlin, Paris. Antwerp and Budapest\neach giving out an advanced price\nfor the cereal almost every day, the\noutlook for dollar wheat could\nscarcely be improved over the pres\nent one."
    }
